{"tid":937066,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揸車的人有福了【青馬大橋驚現廁所】","createTime":"2018-12-11T09:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T10:46:10.000Z","uid":225464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1271125963d3b064c8b6725f0e6bc86a58f69eed","tid":937066,"uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181211/bkn-20181211163538841-1211_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181211%2Fbkn-20181211163538841-1211_00822_001.html&d=VsC9aI3sO9H7xHrCPdzk6IM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=6ab3c77d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181211/bkn-20181211163538841-1211_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oHBUhiP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoHBUhiP.jpg&h=da1e1575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>駕駛者福音？青馬大橋驚現廁所　網民一致讚好</strong><br />\n<br />\n相信不少人坐長途車又或者遇上塞車，最擔心是人有三急，很難找到洗手間方便。但若果公路增設廁所，會否是廣大市民的福音？<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」的片段所見，星期二（11日）下午近2時，青馬大橋的快線突然聳立着一座流動廁所，有男子從廁所後轉出，走向停在中線的貨車。只見貨車車架尚有數座「存貨」，未知廁所是否在駕駛途中意外掉下。<br />\n<br />\n片段引來網民一片好評，戲言︰「香港公路終於有廁所」、「塞車塞得耐，有廁所去都幾好呀」、「初頭我以為曲線話有流動快相，原來堅㗎」。有網民更開玩笑地建議，可在路中加設櫃員機、便利店及汽水機。"},{"pid":"8d005cb464202c6ca0542454a58387574e87927e","tid":937066,"uid":102096,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:58:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bf3019337ac00a0504461bdc81b72d180168bc1","tid":937066,"uid":25971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:59:42.000Z","msg":"青馬有幾可塞車<br />\n係加都加俾屯公啦"},{"pid":"1920d9682814251ddeb9562f9d8e9b5e3d2634b4","tid":937066,"uid":198165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8d005cb464202c6ca0542454a58387574e87927e","tid":937066,"uid":102096,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:58:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T1